# Vox Media's Shared Privacy and Compliance Framework

This code is responsible for supporting the legislation and implementing the frameworks concerning user privacy.



## Rough Diagram

_Initial sketch._


╔════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
║                 CAPABILITIES                   ║
║                                                ║
